"children":"A 12-person independent restaurant was spending 5 hours a week on scheduling — and still overstaffing Tuesdays and getting slammed on Friday nights. Here's the exact workflow they built to fix both."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"w-full h-px bg-[#1e1e1e] mb-12"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-6","children":"The Numbers"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4","children":[["$","div","Labor cost reduction",{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d] p-5","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[28px] font-light text-[#c9a84c] leading-none mb-1","children":"18%"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[11px] text-[#9a9590] mb-1","children":"Labor cost reduction"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#5a5550]","children":"month-over-month"}]]}],["$","div","Monthly savings",{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d] p-5","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[28px] font-light text-[#c9a84c] leading-none mb-1","children":"$$3,400"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[11px] text-[#9a9590] mb-1","children":"Monthly savings"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#5a5550]","children":"on a $19K labor budget"}]]}],["$","div","Scheduling time saved",{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d] p-5","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[28px] font-light text-[#c9a84c] leading-none mb-1","children":"4 hrs/wk"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-[11px] text-[#9a9590] mb-1","children":"Scheduling time saved"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#5a5550]","children":"owner gets it back"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-5","children":"The Problem"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[22px] font-light text-[#f0ede8] mb-4","children":"Scheduling by gut feel was costing $3,400/month"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The owner of a 12-staff Italian restaurant in a mid-sized city was writing the weekly schedule every Sunday morning — 4 to 5 hours of cross-referencing availability, predicting covers, and trying to match staffing to demand. He'd been doing it for 9 years."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The problem: his predictions were based on memory and rough seasonal patterns. He was consistently over-scheduling mid-week — paying 3 servers for a Tuesday that only needed 1.5 — and under-staffing Fridays, which meant slower table turns, worse service scores, and tips that drove turnover."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":"Labor was his biggest controllable expense at ~30% of revenue. A 3-point improvement — from 30% to 27% — would net $3,400/month at his volume. He didn't need a labor scheduling platform at $500/month. He needed a workflow."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-5","children":"The Workflow — 3 Steps"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[22px] font-light text-[#f0ede8] mb-8","children":"Historical data → AI demand forecast → optimized schedule draft"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border-b border-[#1e1e1e] px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#c9a84c]","children":"Step 01"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-1 h-1 bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-full"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"Pull historical covers and revenue — POS export"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-3","children":"Every Sunday, a 2-minute POS export (the restaurant uses Toast) pulls covers and revenue by day and hour for the past 12 weeks. The file is a simple CSV — date, covers, revenue, day of week. No cleanup needed."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":"The owner also notes any upcoming local events (sports games, concerts, school breaks) in a simple running text note."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#5a5550] mt-3","children":"Tool: Toast POS export. Alternative: any POS with CSV export (Square, Lightspeed, Revel)."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border-b border-[#1e1e1e] px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#c9a84c]","children":"Step 02"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-1 h-1 bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-full"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"AI demand forecast — Claude analyzes the CSV"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-3","children":"The CSV and the upcoming events note are pasted into Claude using the prompt below. Claude analyzes the trailing 12-week pattern, identifies day-of-week seasonality, and outputs a predicted covers range for each day of the coming week — with a confidence note and a recommended staffing level for each shift."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":"The output takes about 45 seconds to generate and runs inside Claude.ai — no API or technical setup required."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#5a5550] mt-3","children":"Tool: Claude.ai (Pro tier, $20/mo). Could be Claude API + Zapier for full automation."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border-b border-[#1e1e1e] px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#c9a84c]","children":"Step 03"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-1 h-1 bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-full"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"Coverage optimization — schedule draft in 15 minutes"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-3","children":"With the forecast in hand, the owner pastes staff availability (collected via a WhatsApp poll each Thursday) and asks Claude to generate an optimized schedule draft. Claude maps available staff to forecasted demand shifts, flags under-coverage, and outputs a shift-by-shift roster."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":"The owner spends 15 minutes reviewing and making final adjustments — down from 4–5 hours. The approved schedule goes to staff via 7shifts (free tier) or WhatsApp group."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#5a5550] mt-3","children":"Tools: Claude.ai + 7shifts (free) or any shift-sharing method."}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-5","children":"Full Tool Stack"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d] divide-y divide-[#1e1e1e]","children":[[["$","div","Toast POS",{"className":"px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-between","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"Toast POS"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[12px] text-[#5a5550] ml-3","children":"Historical covers + revenue export"}]]}],["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[12px] text-[#9a959